<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to RavenBoost!</title>
  <style>
    /* Global Styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4B0082; /* RavenBoost Primary Color: Purple */
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header img {
      max-width: 150px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #FFD700; /* RavenBoost Secondary Color: Gold */
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #4B0082; /* Primary Color */
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4B0082; /* Primary Color */
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #4B0082; /* Primary Color */
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #FFD700; /* Gold */
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Email Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://www.ravenboost.com/images/logo.png" alt="RavenBoost Logo"> <!-- Replace with correct logo URL -->
      <h1>Welcome to RavenBoost!</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Email Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi <%= @user.name %>,</h2>
      <p>Thank you for signing up with RavenBoost! We're thrilled to have you as a part of our community.</p>

      <p>At RavenBoost, we strive to provide the best gaming experience with top-notch service. Whether you're leveling up, completing challenges, or simply exploring the community, we are here to support you.</p>

      <p>To get started, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>

      <a href="<%= @verification_link %>" class="button">Verify Your Email</a>

      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>

      <p>Welcome aboard and happy gaming!</p>

      <p>Cheers,<br>The RavenBoost Team</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Â© 2024 RavenBoost. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><a href="https://www.ravenboost.com">Visit our website</a> | <a href="https://www.ravenboost.com/support">Contact Support</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
